{"tid":922592,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬體會鋒線內訌分裂？哥斯達與基沙文現不和「我才是你的隊友！」","createTime":"2018-11-30T13:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T16:07:23.000Z","uid":77606,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"d17b1fae9c35fcf088abcfe10922fab171d9ede7","tid":922592,"uid":77606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:36:24.000Z","msg":"馬德里體育會喺西甲主場以1:1打和巴塞隆拿，錯過升上榜首嘅機會，不過基沙文面對自己人係咪一定要幫呢個問題，佢嘅答案好多Like，網民反而唔覺得，咩事都要盲目幫自己人，相信馬體會喺歐聯分組賽主場對摩納哥，基沙文可以安心備戰。 <br />\n<br />\n話說馬體會對巴塞嘅比賽尾段，迪亞高哥斯達同烏迪姆姆爭波嘈交，仲扯火向球證投訴，基沙文見到即刻埋去勸交，避免衝突擴大，點知迪哥覺得基沙文唔幫佢，西班牙《阿斯報》話佢當時咁講：「我至係你隊友呀！佢唔係！」 <br />\n<br />\n結果基沙文勁無奈，做咗個「你癲咗呀」嘅手勢回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EJ5zfbHufUY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEJ5zfbHufUY&d=Rw8TgxYCWyBNPWI9w6ck19r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8d5d2aca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EJ5zfbHufUY</a>"},{"pid":"db9b6349747e65c561a20469f0b6addeff84343d","tid":922592,"uid":182701,"like":60,"dislike":12,"score":48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:39:31.000Z","msg":"法國隊友唔係隊友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9db99b3cef85b0812fad3ff7bb174d4ace3eb8","tid":922592,"uid":171754,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:40:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1b18f3ae2a96fb6c1d7c671c096ccb373c49622","tid":922592,"uid":141134,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:44:01.000Z","msg":"基沙文遲早過埋巴塞"},{"pid":"1e5dde98b105616c1d691c1242ec6028efa5d5b9","tid":922592,"uid":54025,"like":40,"dislike":94,"score":-54,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:44:29.000Z","msg":"DC真心好有球味<br />\n<br />\n如果依家仲係車仔，真心可以同鏝城一戰"},{"pid":"339719685efd945969a50f9b36b2b676e2cc655f","tid":922592,"uid":196552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:46:00.000Z","msg":"而家先知哥狗癲會唔會太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"